      "value": "克什米尔门具有重要的军事意义"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.faa600b576ca",
      "source": "Keep governance, money, labor, technology, and culture in view.",
      "value": "关注治理、金钱、劳动力、技术和文化。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.3c035f42d26a",
