    },
    {
      "key": "component.cc1188a9f9d7",
      "source": "Legal status shaped daily life",
      "value": "法律地位塑造了日常生活"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.c84cb551d49b",
      "source": "Les Invalides",
      "value": "荣军院"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.60b9fde92081",
      "source": "List what has to be true for the idea to work.",
      "value": "列出该想法要成立必须满足的条件。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.ea5f24224625",
      "source": "Listing the five labels without judging their strength does not explain whether the industry is attractive.",
      "value": "仅列出五个标签而不评估其力度，无法说明该行业是否具有吸引力。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.288608f5b5bb",
      "source": "Literate helper near records, letters, or multilingual exchange",
