      "value": "在委员会中会见安贝德卡尔"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.740c8e2db451",
      "source": "Meet the moment",
      "value": "把握当下"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.5870a8bd3fb4",
      "source": "Merchant assistant",
      "value": "商人助理"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.ddb7e3d07b26",
      "source": "Merchant household scribe",
      "value": "商人家庭书记员"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.aaf86db03034",
      "source": "Merchant lanes",
      "value": "商道"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.07e605d2ffa7",
      "source": "Merge changes",
      "value": "合并更改"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.40609f11ab91",
      "source": "Merge the accepted changes into a clean current version, then update the decision log and open questions.",
      "value": "将已接受的更改合并到当前的整洁版本中，然后更新决策日志和待解决问题。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.fd79cc9ad433",
      "source": "Metic trader",
      "value": "细致的交易者"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.7540943a58b3",
      "source": "Michelangelo's David was installed in 1504",
      "value": "米开朗基罗的《大卫》像于1504年安装"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.57d30c0ba0e0",
      "source": "Middle Chinese",
      "value": "中古汉语"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.f905ffeaa07e",
