      "value": "迷你课程"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.ec7af259de9a",
      "source": "Misses become a smaller review deck",
      "value": "错题将成为一个较小的复习卡组"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.5aae6dac02c6",
      "source": "Missing distinction",
      "value": "缺乏区分"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.1387a4a1f8d1",
      "source": "Missing the curfew or ignoring official rank can quickly become dangerous.",
      "value": "错过宵禁或无视官方等级很快就会变得危险。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.a700fcc41302",
      "source": "Mission pending",
      "value": "任务待定"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.978397428983",
      "source": "Mitosis, climate zones, irregular verbs...",
      "value": "有丝分裂、气候带、不规则动词……"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.936c8b123a7c",
      "source": "Mixes substitutes with direct alternatives.",
      "value": "将替代品与直接替代方案混合使用。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.33598009f19c",
      "source": "Modern assumptions about equal citizenship would be immediately out of place.",
      "value": "关于平等公民身份的现代假设会显得格格不入。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.f3448d205125",
      "source": "Modern talk of individual artistic genius can sound naive without patronage, guild, and civic context.",
      "value": "如果没有赞助、行会和公民背景，关于个人艺术天才的现代谈论听起来可能很天真。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.30c9fc7a107c",
      "source": "Mohenjo-daro around 2500 BCE",
      "value": "公元前2500年左右的摩亨佐-达罗"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.4be4d4906391",
      "source": "Monastery translator",
      "value": "修道院翻译员"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.05e19509b9ee",
      "source": "Moral tribunal",
      "value": "道德法庭"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.1e9f2f5ff601",
      "source": "More immersive, with tighter limits on what you can know and say.",
      "value": "更具沉浸感，对你能知道和说出的内容有更严格的限制。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.2d9ff5969864",
      "source": "Move carefully and notice ordinary life before judging.",
      "value": "在评判之前，请小心行事并观察日常生活。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.68fe9b699576",
      "source": "Move one control, watch the result, then explain why the output changed.",
      "value": "移动一个控件，观察结果，然后解释为什么输出发生了变化。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.4d8cf56f69ad",
      "source": "Move toward final synthesis",
      "value": "迈向最终综合"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.af1804117fe3",
      "source": "Movement needs a plausible errand",
      "value": "行动需要一个合理的理由"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.a7b4e15e1273",
      "source": "Moving every control at once makes it hard to know what caused the result.",
      "value": "同时移动所有控件会让人难以判断是什么导致了结果。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.c21fea88eaab",
      "source": "Moving on after recognition instead of testing recall and transfer.",
      "value": "在识别后继续前进，而不是测试回忆和迁移。"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.7de3804a3ffb",
      "source": "Mughal Empire under Akbar",
      "value": "阿克巴统治下的莫卧儿帝国"
    },
    {
      "key": "component.c8937243bab0",
      "source": "Mughal symbolic authority under rebel control, contested by the East India Company",
